00:01:43.100 --> 00:01:48.060
This will most likely result in what Portugal is going through now, a country with no net neutrality.

00:01:48.060 --> 00:01:50.280
That means saying hello to additional tiers and fees!

00:01:50.280 --> 00:01:55.520
Use Facebook, YouTube, Gmail, and Spotify? Guess what? You're in for additional tiers now!

00:01:55.520 --> 00:01:57.720
