00:02:03.300 --> 00:02:07.100
go to battle for the net dot com (battleforthenet.com) and call your members of the House and Senate.

00:02:07.100 --> 00:02:10.720
And then go to your state's website and find your local representative and call them.

00:02:10.720 --> 00:02:13.859
And just tell them you want net neutrality passed in your state.

00:02:13.860 --> 00:02:16.560
